welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Powell, a charming city known for its breathtaking scenery and friendly locals. Get ready to discover all the beauty and excitement this city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ohio State University Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Port Columbus International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A primarily serves domestic flights operated by American Airlines.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B serves domestic flights operated by Delta, Southwest, and United Airlines.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C serves domestic and international flights operated by Frontier, Spirit, and Allegiant Airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. No password is required.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Rickenbacker Airport handles all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Rickenbacker Airport is a major hub for air freight and is equipped with state-of-the-art facilities.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport houses all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Municipal Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
